    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable Project Car \u2014 Priced to Move! If you're a hands-on buyer looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper or a solid parts source, this could be just what you need! This car is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant mechanical issues and visible wear, so it's best suited for someone with repair experience or a specific project in mind. The price reflects the condition honestly, giving you a great starting point without overpaying. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
